display="inline"><![CDATA[u{\downarrow }=\top ]]></fr:tex>.</fr:blockquote>

  <fr:p>This follows from the <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://github.com/jonsterling/coq-domains/blob/main/theories/Path.v">(constructive) characterization</fr:link> of the <fr:link
